Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 1016 16th Street, NW is a historic building that is located near The White House. There are three approximately 4,400 RSF floors available in the building on the 3rd, 4th, and 5th floors for a total of 13,200 RSF for lease or sale. For sale, the condo fees as of 2018 are $13.27 and $10.38 in taxes. The PSF rate is $550/PRF. For lease, the spaces are available between 1 and ten years.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Historic Building Steps Away from White House
